column2: SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, ts.SchoolYear4Digit, ts.TestPeriod, ts.TestSubjectGroup, &&&,ts.TestType, ts.TestScore   FROM Enrollment e    INNER JOIN TestScores ts    ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID    INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe     ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID     INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es     ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID        union all   SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, pe.SchoolYear4Digit, CONVERT(int,&&&), &&&,&&& ,&&&,   SELECT x.SUM(pe.hours) FROM (SELECT pe.SchoolYear4Digit, SUM(pe.hours) FROM ParentEngagement pe GROUP BY pe.SchoolYear4Digit) AS x)   FROM Enrollment e    INNER JOIN TestScores ts    ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID    INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe     ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID     INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es     ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID        union all      SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID, e.GradeLevel, es.SchoolYear4Digit, es.Period,&&&, &&&, &&&, es.Score    FROM Enrollment e    INNER JOIN TestScores ts    ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID    INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe     ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID     INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es     ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID
